          <li><strong>Reference fields:</strong> Link related content items</li>
          <li><strong>Multi-item pages:</strong> Generate pages from CMS items</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Perfect for:</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Blogs with complex categorization</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Product catalogs with variants</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Team directories with roles</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Event calendars with filtering</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Case study libraries</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
