          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Simple blogs (use Squarespace)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Basic pages (use any builder)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Static content</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Users who don't need complexity</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Pros and Cons -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Webflow Pros and Cons</h2>

